commitResults.messageTitle: Update Cycle to allow for hyphens
commitResults.messageBody:
Currently, Cycle only accepts alphanumeric characters.

We want Cycle to accept hyphens as valid input
e.g. "Off-cycle 2025"

Let's update the regex and test cases for Cycle.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add find command to user guide
commitResults.messageBody:
Find command was previously removed from the original AB3
user guide.

The find command will be used in the new InternTracker application.

Let's,
add the find command back to the user guide.

AB3 Behaviour for search is based on keywords using
the CompanyContainsKeywordPredicate class.
Search "Jane" -> "Jane street"
Search "Google Meta" will match "Google" and "Meta"

Let's update the find command to be more intuitive for searching company names.
Specifically, let's
Create a new class called CompanyPartialMatchPredicate which
has the following behaviour
Search "jan" -> "Jane Street"
Search "JAN" -> "Jane Street"
Search "jst" -> "Jane Street"
Search "Google Meta" doesnâ€™t match anything
